<td width="150"><br></td>
<td align="center"><b>
<i>Perdita vespertina</i> <font size="-1" face="sans-serif">Griswold and Miller, 2010</font></b><br>
<a href="/mp/20q?search=Life">Life</a>
&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/mp/20q?search=Insecta">Insecta</a>
&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/mp/20q?search=Hymenoptera">Hymenoptera</a>
&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/mp/20q?search=Apoidea">Apoidea</a>
&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/mp/20q?search=Andrenidae">Andrenidae</a>
&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/mp/20q?search=Perdita">Perdita</a>
<br><small>Subgenus: <a href="/mp/20p?see=Xerophasma&name=Perdita&flags=subgenus:"><i>Xerophasma</i></a></small>
</td></tr></table><p>
<p>
<table width="80%" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" border="0"><tr><td>
<div align="center">
<table><tr><td valign="top" align="center"><a href="/mp/20m?kind=Perdita+vespertina"><img src="/nh/maps/Insecta/Hymenoptera/Apoidea/Andrenidae/Perdita/map_of_Perdita_vespertina.jpg" width="360" height="180" border="0"></a><br><font color="red" size="-1" face="sans-serif">Click on map for details about points.</font>
<p><div align="center"><table border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" width="50%"><tr><td nowrap><b>IDnature guide</b></td></tr><tr><td nowrap><ul><li><a href="/mp/20q?guide=Apoidea_species&flags=HAS:" target="_top">
